J. D. Williams https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/J._D._Williams 0 Darnell "J.D." Williams (born May 22, 1978) is an American actor from New Jersey. Best known for his starring roles in the HBO television programs Oz as Kenny Wangler, The Wire as Bodie Broadus and Pootie Tang as Froggy.
